00:22:22,720 --> 00:22:24,279
and he would come home every week.

282
00:22:24,839 --> 00:22:27,160
Sometimes he would be gone for a few weeks

283
00:22:27,920 --> 00:22:29,759
or even months.

284
00:22:32,599 --> 00:22:34,640
I'm not coming back to Bangkok
this weekend.

285
00:22:34,720 --> 00:22:35,960
Again?

286
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:38,480
But it's my birthday this Saturday.

287
00:22:39,440 --> 00:22:40,799
Saen?

288
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:42,960
Saen?

289
00:22:44,079 --> 00:22:45,000
Hello?

290
00:23:03,039 --> 00:23:04,640
Did you get cut off?

291
00:23:05,759 --> 00:23:08,359
Saen is in a meeting.

292
00:23:08,440 --> 00:23:10,559
Do you have a message for him?

293
00:23:10,640 --> 00:23:13,000
Please let it be about work only, though,

294
00:23:13,079 --> 00:23:15,119
because he's working right now.

295
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,759
I'm sorry.

296
00:23:17,319 --> 00:23:18,960
I'll call again later.

297
00:23:25,599 --> 00:23:27,200
Since that year,

298
00:23:28,279 --> 00:23:30,880
