584
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:04,760
Hurry up.

585
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:05,760
Come on.

586
00:41:07,360 --> 00:41:08,559
Juea.

587
00:41:08,639 --> 00:41:09,519
What now?

588
