706
00:53:17,559 --> 00:53:18,880
I don't even know what it is.

707
00:53:20,960 --> 00:53:22,679
Can you teach me how to use Facebook?

708
00:53:26,199 --> 00:53:27,559
You said that

709
00:53:28,039 --> 00:53:30,000
if I remember who I am,

710
00:53:31,199 --> 00:53:32,719
I have to leave.

711
00:53:34,639 --> 00:53:36,920
I want to record my time with you,

712
00:53:37,480 --> 00:53:39,119
so it can be my memory.

713
00:54:03,519 --> 00:54:04,760
Cut.

714
00:54:04,840 --> 00:54:06,519
That's a wrap!

715
00:54:06,599 --> 00:54:08,039
Good job, everyone.

716
00:54:08,599 --> 00:54:10,840
See you next week.

717
00:54:12,800 --> 00:54:13,639
