724
00:54:39,360 --> 00:54:40,599
Out of a hundred.

725
00:54:42,280 --> 00:54:44,039
Hey, that's not true.

726
00:54:44,119 --> 00:54:47,559
I got through every scene in two
to three takes. Even Juea said I was good.

727
00:54:47,639 --> 00:54:49,719
How can you give me just ten?

728
00:54:49,800 --> 00:54:51,880
You've already complimented yourself.

729
00:54:51,960 --> 00:54:53,119
You need me to do it too?

730
00:54:53,199 --> 00:54:55,519
Well, I want you to praise me.

731
00:55:00,519 --> 00:55:01,960
Doesn't your dad do that?

732
00:55:02,719 --> 00:55:03,840
What do you need me for?

733
00:55:11,199 --> 00:55:12,400
Song,

734
00:55:13,000 --> 00:55:15,159
please go get changed.

735
00:55:15,719 --> 00:55:16,679
Yes.

736
00:55:31,159 --> 00:55:32,239
Hey, Song,

737
00:55:33,039 --> 00:55:34,960
come eat with us.

738
00:55:35,039 --> 00:55:35,960
