739
00:55:36,039 --> 00:55:37,679
no thanks, Juea.

740
00:55:37,760 --> 00:55:39,800
I have to go submit a report.

741
00:55:39,880 --> 00:55:41,760
Okay then.

742
00:55:41,840 --> 00:55:42,960
See you next week.

743
00:55:43,039 --> 00:55:44,559
