757
00:56:38,599 --> 00:56:40,199
Just ride your bike home.

758
00:56:40,280 --> 00:56:42,079
How can I?

759
00:56:42,159 --> 00:56:43,840
I left it at home.

760
00:56:45,039 --> 00:56:47,199
I knew you would drive here,

761
00:56:47,840 --> 00:56:50,199
so I didn't bring my bike.

762
00:56:53,400 --> 00:56:55,440
