1122
01:24:17,600 --> 01:24:19,920
Well, the best way
to get over your old love

1123
01:24:20,439 --> 01:24:22,000
is to find a new one, right?

1124
01:24:23,600 --> 01:24:24,800
If you're happy,

1125
01:24:25,279 --> 01:24:27,840
those romantic scenes
you're struggling with

1126
01:24:28,560 --> 01:24:29,960
will come to you naturally.

1127
01:24:32,680 --> 01:24:34,000
That's easier said than done.

1128
01:24:34,800 --> 01:24:36,520
I've been looking,

1129
01:24:36,600 --> 01:24:38,079
but I haven't found anyone.

1130
01:24:38,159 --> 01:24:39,359
You know that.

1131
01:24:41,359 --> 01:24:42,760
Shall I find someone for you?

1132
01:24:42,840 --> 01:24:43,800
It's easy.

1133
01:24:43,880 --> 01:24:45,439
Two people you know,

1134
01:24:45,520 --> 01:24:46,920
they're crazy about you.

1135
01:24:48,720 --> 01:24:50,319
It's either Prib or Tofu.

1136
01:24:53,199 --> 01:24:55,000
I'm sorry, Prib.

1137
01:24:55,720 --> 01:24:57,680
You cooked for Nut,

1138
01:24:57,760 --> 01:24:59,520
but I made him angry,

1139
01:25:00,279 --> 01:25:01,600
so…

1140
01:25:02,840 --> 01:25:04,199
It's fine.

1141
01:25:05,239 --> 01:25:06,520
It's not your fault.

1142
01:25:07,199 --> 01:25:08,439
Not Nut's fault either.

1143
01:25:09,399 --> 01:25:10,760
It was an accident.

1144
01:25:10,840 --> 01:25:12,239
I understand.

1145
01:25:13,039 --> 01:25:14,479
I can cook again another time.

1146
01:25:29,039 --> 01:25:31,039
It's okay. I'll clean it up.

1147
01:25:37,840 --> 01:25:39,159
By the way,

1148
01:25:39,239 --> 01:25:41,560
how come Nut's work
has to be revised so much?

1149
01:25:42,399 --> 01:25:43,439
Do you know?

1150
01:25:44,720 --> 01:25:47,920
Juea said his romantic scenes
still aren't good enough.

1151
01:25:48,800 --> 01:25:51,119
I guess his past is pretty bitter.

1152
01:25:53,079 --> 01:25:54,359
What does his past

1153
01:25:54,960 --> 01:25:56,600
have to do with his work?

1154
01:25:56,680 --> 01:25:58,560
He's writing about his life.

1155
01:25:59,039 --> 01:26:00,880
Even if it's a little sad,

1156
01:26:01,680 --> 01:26:02,600
that's okay,

1157
01:26:02,680 --> 01:26:05,880
because I'll add sweetness to his life,

1158
01:26:06,960 --> 01:26:08,760
and then things will go well.

1159
01:26:17,680 --> 01:26:18,960
I'm sorry, Prib.

1160
01:26:20,680 --> 01:26:21,880
You too, Tofu.

1161
01:26:23,159 --> 01:26:24,520
Sorry for losing my temper.

1162
01:26:26,159 --> 01:26:27,640
It's okay, Nut.

1163
01:26:27,720 --> 01:26:29,800
I understand everything.

1164
01:26:29,880 --> 01:26:32,239
I'll make you fried pork another time.

1165
01:26:32,319 --> 01:26:34,720
You can look forward to that.

1166
01:26:40,279 --> 01:26:41,359
Something wrong, Gen?

1167
01:26:41,840 --> 01:26:43,119
I have an emergency.

1168
01:26:43,199 --> 01:26:45,359
Sorry, Prib. Go home by yourself.

1169
01:26:45,439 --> 01:26:46,520
What?

1170
01:26:54,439 --> 01:26:55,840
Nut.

1171
01:26:59,439 --> 01:27:00,720
All right,

1172
01:27:02,119 --> 01:27:03,319
I'll call you a taxi.

1173
01:27:19,880 --> 01:27:21,279
You're doing this again, Mom!

1174
01:27:23,159 --> 01:27:24,680
When will you understand

1175
01:27:25,239 --> 01:27:27,560
that going into someone's room
without permission

1176
01:27:27,640 --> 01:27:29,439
is an invasion of privacy?

1177
01:27:43,399 --> 01:27:44,520
What are you doing?

1178
01:27:47,399 --> 01:27:49,199
I just want to know what you wrote.

1179
01:27:52,079 --> 01:27:53,960
What I write is my business.

1180
01:28:09,760 --> 01:28:11,319
NEXT EPISODE

1181
01:28:11,399 --> 01:28:12,760
Mister.

1182
01:28:13,359 --> 01:28:14,600
Song!

1183
01:28:17,159 --> 01:28:19,079
I didn't mean to cause any trouble.

1184
01:28:19,159 --> 01:28:21,119
But you chose to get involved.

1185
01:28:21,199 --> 01:28:24,239
I hope you can put an end
to this problem soon

1186
01:28:24,319 --> 01:28:26,039
without affecting our work.

1187
01:28:27,479 --> 01:28:29,039
Mrs. Na!

1188
01:28:33,359 --> 01:28:34,840
Are you happy, Nut?

1189
01:28:38,319 --> 01:28:39,279
Woo-hoo!

1190
01:28:39,760 --> 01:28:41,159
Your lips…

1191
01:28:43,600 --> 01:28:45,359
are sweet and soft like jelly.

1192
01:28:45,439 --> 01:28:47,159
Why do you sound like…

1193
01:28:48,000 --> 01:28:49,000
Who the hell are you?

1194
01:28:50,920 --> 01:28:52,359
Why are you doing this?

1195
01:28:52,920 --> 01:28:54,640
What do you want from me?

1196
01:29:49,640 --> 01:29:54,640
